Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,到京都了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.94,0:02:03.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是傳說中讓人往下跳的地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.20,0:02:04.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,讓誰跳下去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.03,0:02:05.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 在下就…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.28,0:02:07.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不要亂來…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.80,0:02:09.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是清水寺的本堂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.67,0:02:12.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是俗稱的「清水之舞臺」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:17.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,本來是為供奉的觀音菩薩像 表演能劇和舞蹈而建造
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:17.49,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,(注：能劇為一種日本的傳統戲劇)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:19.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,已經被列為國寶級
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.68,0:02:23.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有句名句叫「打算從清水之舞臺跳下去」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.25,0:02:27.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在江戶時代就有234次跳下去的記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.41,0:02:30.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,存活率居然意外的達到了85%之多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.03,0:02:31.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是個奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.95,0:02:34.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夕映可是神社 寺廟 佛像的發燒友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:38.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在「修學旅行」 裏面有個「學」字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.57,0:02:40.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說這也是教學的一環
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.04,0:02:44.46,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.69,0:02:47.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠一起來 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.32,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 修學旅行真是太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:59.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 如果高畑老師也能一起來就完美了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:00.68,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這也沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:03.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,他是一年級的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.16,0:03:04.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.69,0:03:06.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉 一起去抽籤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.06,0:03:08.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…啊…等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:11.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.43,0:03:19.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真懷念呢 小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:22.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒回京都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.54,0:03:25.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喏 和當初我們兩個人一起玩時沒怎麼變呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:30.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候每天每天都玩得好高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:32.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那時我們還沒有上學…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:34.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,先失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.84,0:03:40.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:46.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在那些傢伙在清水寺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.83,0:03:48.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾呢 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.76,0:03:51.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,您因為登校地獄的詛咒而不能去修學旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.49,0:03:53.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 有什麼可遺憾的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你自己去不好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:59.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我想要一直陪伴在主人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.61,0:04:01.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.88,0:04:07.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快看啊 是緣分占卜的神社
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.83,0:04:09.72,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 快去快去
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.43,0:04:13.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,30分鐘後要回入口處集合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.80,0:04:16.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:17.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個交給你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.24,0:04:20.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:22.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,學院長爺爺拜託的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.78,0:04:24.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,遇到困難的時候可以靠這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:29.81,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…要送到關西咒術協會總部的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.16,0:04:31.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有介紹信…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:34.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？關西咒術協會不是敵人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.27,0:04:38.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 只是其中叫做封眼寺派的一部分人在惹事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:41.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,關西咒術協會本身…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:43.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉 快走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.29,0:04:46.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有戀愛占卜石哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.24,0:04:53.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？只要閉上眼睛 從這塊石頭走到那塊石頭的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.30,0:04:54.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,戀愛就會順利是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.92,0:04:55.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好遠
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.73,0:04:58.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多有20米遠吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.26,0:05:01.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就由身為班長的我開始吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.50,0:05:04.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好狡猾哦 我也要走過去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.19,0:05:05.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也要…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.07,0:05:06.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.46,0:05:08.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.89,0:05:13.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,書店 不是那邊啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:16.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然對不起大家
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.62,0:05:17.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但這種程度的試練
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.06,0:05:21.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對精通各種武藝 並取得了各種段位證明的我來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:22.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不算什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.20,0:05:25.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雪廣綾香流·戀愛心眼術
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.51,0:05:33.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:35.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 班長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.43,0:05:36.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,班長耍賴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.87,0:05:37.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好快
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:41.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣涅吉老師和我的將來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:43.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就能夠確定下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:44.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:46.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:49.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好像踩到了軟軟的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.35,0:05:52.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:57.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊！青青青…青蛙！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:03.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,青蛙？怎麼這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.56,0:06:05.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不要放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這可能只是在分散我們的注意力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.58,0:06:08.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.23,0:06:11.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了 信還在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:15.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:16.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.12,0:06:18.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 那是「式神」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.03,0:06:19.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,「式神」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:22.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 日本的一種召喚魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:24.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不 應該說是紙制的魔偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.35,0:06:39.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？櫻咲同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.81,0:06:40.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我揀到的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.92,0:06:42.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那是我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.07,0:06:45.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的好意…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:48.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小心一些會比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.82,0:06:52.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是京都 可不是麻帆良學院
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.42,0:06:55.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.95,0:06:57.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要感謝她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.23,0:06:59.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.60,0:07:00.25,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.58,0:07:02.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那只鳥的紙型
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.38,0:07:04.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說她是施術者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.60,0:07:06.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…櫻咲同學她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她很可能是我們的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.15,0:07:22.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夕映 要出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.42,0:07:33.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.79,0:07:35.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我們來玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:42.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和香 明天的自由時間你要幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:43.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.24,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,和涅吉老師一起逛京都吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.21,0:07:49.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,枕頭大戰是一定要玩的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.48,0:07:53.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要玩一定要玩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.18,0:08:01.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？櫻咲同學是敵人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不 只是懷疑而已…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.92,0:08:07.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯的 她就是封眼寺派的手下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:09.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.66,0:08:14.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 聽說櫻咲同學和木乃香是青梅竹馬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？是那樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.42,0:08:19.71,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒見過那兩個人彼此說過話啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:22.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香的確這樣說過的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:26.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,總之 危機就近在眼前了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.77,0:08:29.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想請大姐來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.33,0:08:30.21,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.38,0:08:32.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐 這個還記得嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.69,0:08:35.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我和明日菜同學定下暫訂契約的時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.59,0:08:39.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…不要讓我回想起那種害羞的事啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.63,0:08:40.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:43.08,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是普通的卡片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐只要念「阿德阿特」 就可以變出武器！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:46.57,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(272,410)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.20,0:08:48.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你想讓我參加戰鬥？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 不行啦 對手可是會用魔法的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:56.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是普通的女中學生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不是不是 最近的女中學生不容小看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:02.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,特別是在這2-A裏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.15,0:09:04.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,確實 依文潔琳同學和楓同學都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:06.09,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.30,0:09:12.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.75,0:09:16.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 不知道為什麼沒有反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.15,0:09:19.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,唔 真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:24.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候 直接用手就可以了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.21,0:09:27.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真不愧是大姐 完全是蠻力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.45,0:09:28.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.41,0:09:31.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是不好意思 太感謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.57,0:09:33.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不用 是不是出故障了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.85,0:09:37.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真傷腦筋呢 我會和旅館的人說的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.41,0:09:47.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是謝謝你放我進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.98,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可愛的西洋魔法使先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喔喔 這個就夢幻商品抹茶可樂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.20,0:10:01.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,夕映還是這麼喜歡奇怪的飲料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:04.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是小刹喜歡的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.59,0:10:06.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里啊 木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:08.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我去告訴小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.07,0:10:10.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.14,0:10:12.77,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害 這就是露天浴場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.11,0:10:21.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,被風吹著真舒服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:25.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 要是沒有關於櫻咲刹那的煩心事就更好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.53,0:10:30.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有人來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:32.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位老師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.99,0:10:37.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻…櫻咲同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.92,0:10:39.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏不是男浴場麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:41.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這裏是混浴啊 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:46.55,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 這樣結界就佈置完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:48.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,在幹什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:50.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.75,0:10:51.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她可是劍士
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.12,0:10:55.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有夥伴的近身戰對大哥十分不利
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.34,0:10:56.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呃…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.97,0:10:58.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但話說回來還是不好辦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.19,0:11:02.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,本來還指望作為魔法使的老師 能夠做點什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.37,0:11:04.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.77,0:11:06.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼知道我是魔法使的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.00,0:11:09.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,刹那那傢伙 果然是敵人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.00,0:11:14.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,被發現了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.88,0:11:16.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.95,0:11:17.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想逃走嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,神鳴流奧義·斬岩劍！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.13,0:11:27.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 救命！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:28.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,卡莫！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.05,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾·馬斯吉爾·馬吉斯泰爾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.11,0:11:32.05,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,風花·武裝解除
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.57,0:11:34.67,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,FLANS  EXARMATIO
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.00,0:11:38.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,厲害 大哥把那傢伙的武器擊落了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.97,0:11:42.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:44.58,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不回答的話就捏爛掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.22,0:11:55.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你是什麼人！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不回答的話就捏爛掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:02.22,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 涅吉老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.55,0:12:05.28,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 老師
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不…這只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:13.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我工作中理論上是一定要攻擊要害的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:18.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻咲刹那！你這傢伙果然是封眼寺派的手下啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼…不是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:23.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,現在證據確鑿了 你給我準備好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:25.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我不是敵人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.40,0:12:27.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我和老師同一陣線的！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.73,0:12:35.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹如果看到那個點心的話一定會很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.49,0:12:46.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎到來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.84,0:12:50.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:51.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐的聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.08,0:12:55.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 猴子？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.00,0:12:57.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,明日菜同學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:12:59.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香大小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.73,0:13:06.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只要把木乃香大小姐奪到手 我們就…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.20,0:13:08.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.52,0:13:14.48,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太過糾纏的話會被討厭的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.92,0:13:16.79,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,壞了 要逃進車站了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.95,0:13:22.59,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是停運時間 但怎麼連一個站務人員都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.04,0:13:24.76,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,她張貼了不讓人靠近的符咒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:27.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的目標是木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是一開始就計畫好了的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.29,0:13:32.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要針對木乃香？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.89,0:13:33.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香大小姐她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.54,0:13:37.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,潛藏有極東地區最強的魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.72,0:13:38.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.98,0:13:41.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,甚至能與Thousand master相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:42.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.75,0:13:44.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,魔力的話…那就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:47.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香大小姐是魔法使嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:49.26,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐自己並沒意識到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.56,0:13:52.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 敵人看來已經知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.04,0:13:57.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,涅吉老師 把她逼到前面的車廂去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,符咒啊符咒 幫助我擺脫對方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.35,0:14:15.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這些水是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:26.41,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…可別淹死在這裏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.09,0:14:31.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 居然被敵人這樣輕易的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:35.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的技術…果然還不夠成熟
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:37.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香大小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.42,0:14:41.94,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,斬空閃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.70,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還很不錯的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.87,0:14:56.57,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我可不會把大小姐還給你們哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,木乃香大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:01.99,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把木乃香大小姐還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:22.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喲 居然能追到這裏來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.25,0:15:25.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 也只能到此為止了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,封眼寺派的麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:33.67,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,符咒啊符咒 幫助我擺脫對方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.93,0:15:35.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.42,0:15:39.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,三枚符咒術·京都大文字燒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.97,0:15:45.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:48.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能力普通的施術者 是沒辦法穿過這些火焰的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾·馬斯吉爾·馬吉斯泰爾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.76,0:15:50.84,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,風花·風塵亂舞
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.78,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,FLANS  SALTATIO  PULVEREA
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我的火焰居然被吹滅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:05.14,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是西洋魔法使的力量嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:07.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,把大小姐還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:19.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種招式…神鳴流？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:22.07,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真對不起 我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.20,0:16:28.86,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你好 我是神鳴流的 初次見面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.85,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是…神鳴流劍士？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.02,0:16:34.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我叫月詠
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:39.45,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去您也是神鳴流的前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:41.64,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不過既然我被雇來做護衛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還是要全力以赴的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.32,0:16:48.60,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情神鳴流也做…時代也變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.99,0:16:49.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.80,0:16:51.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太小看她的話可使會受傷的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.85,0:16:52.78,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,月詠小妹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.19,0:16:56.75,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 那麼我就上了 請手下留情哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.66,0:17:06.61,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,出乎意外的強
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.58,0:17:08.40,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,刹那同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:11.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你們的對手在這裏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.81,0:17:15.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小熊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:17.53,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,猴子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.65,0:17:18.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,布偶自己在動啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.25,0:17:21.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,請小心一點 從外表上是看不出它們很強的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾·馬斯吉爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.35,0:17:23.42,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel ma scir…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:24.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.27,0:17:24.84,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.90,0:17:26.34,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.96,0:17:32.74,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈哈 我的猿鬼和熊鬼可是很強的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,壞了 即使是大哥以一敵二的話也…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.28,0:17:38.19,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好色雪貂 那咒文是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.47,0:17:39.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.20,0:17:41.43,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 能變出武器的那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.63,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(307,410)}Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.57,0:17:43.63,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是「阿德阿特」啊 大姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.26,0:17:45.30,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,阿德阿特
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:47.06,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,Adeat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.55,0:17:54.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.73,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:57.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是把摺扇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:17:59.23,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:02.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,大姐的卡片上的確寫的是「破魔之劍」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:03.95,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.61,0:18:07.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法了 上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:15.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.88,0:18:19.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼 我的猿鬼居然被送回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.05,0:18:20.83,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.11,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不知道是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:23.33,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,但這只熊就交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.47,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你去救木乃香
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.52,0:18:26.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.39,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,拉斯泰爾·馬斯吉爾·馬吉斯泰爾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:28.39,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,ras tel ma scir magister
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,魔法之射手·警戒之風矢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.62,0:18:31.73,yingwen,,0000,0000,0000,,SAGITTA  MAGICA,AER  CAPTURAE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.26,0:18:36.04,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.43,0:18:37.18,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,回來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.54,0:18:41.34,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.66,0:18:45.32,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,快放開木乃香同學
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.52,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:49.20,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 你太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.30,0:18:51.51,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然因為顧及人質而不攻擊我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:56.69,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊哈哈…這個女孩還真有用呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.23,0:18:58.97,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,既可以作人質
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.16,0:19:01.49,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還可以作「發電機」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.68,0:19:02.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你說「發電機」？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:06.44,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 只要用咒術和符咒讓她聽話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:09.27,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,按我們的意願釋放魔力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:12.02,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以成為我們的魔力發電機了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.03,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.84,0:19:16.93,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:21.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,還有 不聽話的小鬼可要打屁股哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.77,0:19:26.87,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,居然對木乃香大小姐…做這種事！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.29,0:19:28.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.91,0:19:31.65,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,秘劍·百花撩亂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:41.54,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:44.16,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.12,0:19:57.29,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:00.50,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:03.01,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 小刹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.79,0:20:05.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不清楚出了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.69,0:20:06.96,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,是你救了我吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我…我失禮了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.45,0:20:12.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:15.00,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.18,0:20:16.89,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.22,0:20:18.06,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,小刹？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.16,0:20:19.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,刹那同學 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.58,0:20:40.42,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,被你救了呢 新人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.15,0:20:42.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,眼鏡眼鏡 我的眼鏡…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.53,0:20:41.62,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,有一手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,Thousand master的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.53,0:20:52.35,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,只有那種程度而已嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.60,0:21:09.17,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 喂喂 我是近右衛門
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.79,0:21:11.88,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,哦 是刹那啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:16.90,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？封眼寺派的咒術使？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.13,0:21:22.12,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,不…只是現在要立刻派增援過去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:23.36,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.14,0:22:59.56,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 班長會合氣道對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:03.31,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不過僅僅達到了「免許皆傳」的程度而已
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.68,0:23:03.31,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,(免許皆傳：級別的一種，強於「上級」)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:05.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能教給我一些簡單的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.83,0:23:07.84,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼先教一些小技巧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.03,0:23:10.10,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,就是扳住腰和腿再投擲出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.16,0:23:12.82,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,扳住嗎…我知道了 做做試試看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.63,0:23:14.73,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼搞！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.82,0:23:18.80,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我把手從你嘴裏伸進去捏碎你的喉*嗎 笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:21.92,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,蒔繪同學 這可就不是「扳住」而是「切斷」了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.07,0:23:23.15,zhengwen,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？！
